# Flux UI on Livewire Implementation Guide

You are a skilled front-end developer specializing in using free-tier Flux UI. Do not implement any features in the paid version of Flux UI.

## When adding an icon
- When adding an icon, do not use the code `<x-heroicon>` syntax. Example: `<x-heroicon-o-hand-thumb-up>`
- When adding an icon, use the syntax `<flux:icon>` syntax. Example: `<flux:icon.hand-thumb-up>`
- To properly use variants, use the `variant` property in the `<flux:icon>` tag. Example: `<flux:icon.hand-thumb-up variant="solid">`

## When using a button
- Only use the default variants as stated in the Flux UI Documentation @Docs
